{"tid":2252508,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"梵蒂岡證實將與中國延長主教任命協議兩年","createTime":"2020-10-21T13:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T13:24:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"000761a1beb086169cce6c77f8152445889caa2e","tid":2252508,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:27:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】梵蒂岡國務卿帕羅林樞機證實，將會與中國延長主教任命臨時協議兩年。<br />\n<br />\n雙方達成的主教任命臨時協議將於周四屆滿，帕羅林證實，協議會延長兩年。他被記者追問時，承認協議已經談妥；又說所有事會順利落實。<br />\n<br />\n中國和梵蒂岡在2018年9月，簽署主教任命臨時協議，為期兩年，梵蒂岡有任命內地主教的最終決定權。<br />\n<br />\n帕羅林又透露，中梵是在過去幾日達成延長協議的決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=409958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D409958&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPaxOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=e3d55692\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D409958&h=28c543c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=409958</a>"},{"pid":"b2361f21de211beedd163e9f9e942e376714aa59","tid":2252508,"uid":279333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:28:32.000Z","msg":"dklm<br />\n<br />\n等落地獄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c1c613a09b44a2484d8700f0c1906d8fba21b8","tid":2252508,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2361f21de211beedd163e9f9e942e376714aa59","tid":2252508,"uid":279333,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:28:32.000Z","msg":"dklm<br />\n<br />\n等落地獄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202